Prerequistes:
- checkit.pl and resulting ipa commands must be run on an IPA enrolled host

provisioning/rbac/checkit.pl : provisioning script
 - provides commands to create new namespace RBAC and associated user and group objects
 - evaluate existing namespace RBAC; provide commands to perform changes

./checkit.pl -h
usage:
     validate all namespace; display only ipa commands
      : ./checkit.pl 

     validate all namespace; verbose output
      : ./checkit.pl -t

     validate specific namespace; display only ipa commands
      : ./checkit.pl -n=acme

     validate specific namespace; display and write ipa commands to acme.sh
      : ./checkit.pl -n=acme | tee acme.sh

     validate specific namespace; verbose output
      : ./checkit.pl -n=acme -t

Permission Templates:
  provisioning/config/admin : namespace admin role
  provisioning/config/owner : namespace owner role
  provisioning/config/owner : amespace hostenroll user role used for automating host enrollment

RBAC Modules:
  provisioning/lib/IDM/RBAC/Common.pm : common functions
  provisioning/lib/IDM/RBAC/Admin.pm : namespace admin role functions
  provisioning/lib/IDM/RBAC/Owner.pm : namespace owner role functions
  provisioning/lib/IDM/RBAC/Hostenroll.pm : namespace owner role functions
